Summary: Looking out my truck window at a clearing in the clouds, when this object darted across the clearing of the clouds.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at a scrap facility waiting in line. I was looking at the clouds, and saw this oval shaped object dart across the clearing of the clouds. I was surprised because it had no wings,was shiny silver colored an moved fast.
